  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>패키지, 박스 소량 생산</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cdcdf6e0-4a2f-4c3f-bd26-f87ae9e62372\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-595680ce-2561-4132-8392-588a1982af59\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223939367562/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">검정 3단 싸바리 박스</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-76ee4081-bf36-45bb-8d12-9105af77c4c5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223939367562/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cca9892b-8035-4ca7-9dfa-de85e79ab0b2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-12da4382-d46e-4a30-b777-c5a7a5f29028\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f1c9039f-5b37-43d3-9e97-89b5b45e3fa9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">3단 싸바리 박스는 제품에 융단을 깔고 제품을 담는 용도로 제작됩니다. 가장 비싼 박스 중에 하나이고 최고급으로 제작되는 포장재이기 때문에 저렴하게 만들기보다는 조금 더 고급스럽게 만드는 것이 좋습니다. 단가가 비싸기 때문에 소량 생산은 거의 불가능합니다. 정확하게 말하자면 불가능하기보다는 고객님께서 손해(?)십니다. 개당 단가가 올라가기 때문입니다. 경험상 최소 5,000개 이상 제작하지 않으면 개당 단가는 소량과 차이가 많이 납니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b9609036-00c1-4c2c-a234-7188674357c2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-22664d19-527f-4700-812c-e79149a2d88f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-878d2fc2-68f7-48cf-9735-b39b9118147b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ace42250-55df-43e9-9e22-dc5149592054\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>3단 싸바리 박스의 구성</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-14364abc-fe42-4847-b32c-02592bb9a634\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-aabffcee-d4dd-400b-8594-76c600a0963a\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8da7a5f-afca-43dd-922e-668de32db9bd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-301bcd4c-bb33-417e-b650-a7bb95a810a1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>상짝</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0034bf6c-8572-4667-ad05-522c4e9ec135\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f91eeae6-2f66-466b-927a-58606b70c3ef\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 뚜껑을 말합니다. 위 뚜껑의 면에 인쇄를 하거나 로고를 삽입하는 경우가 많습니다. 백지나 일반 종이에는 4도 인쇄를 하는 경우도 많지만 위 샘플과 같이 흑지에는 백색 인쇄, 실크, 형압으로 처리하는 것이 보통입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-71be752e-d460-4b96-84fc-a76c6f385ba9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cb8f249d-a53c-4025-bb53-c1ec7910ce05\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ed08ab4e-3552-4460-a5c7-b7fe3d32fc84\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4493ec13-728a-4f51-8977-9904abe38f7a\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>인쇄지 + 갱판지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-91002726-3ef2-4e41-b9e4-6ab3242f92b5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a784a4d9-b270-40df-8667-ff69ba2c9b7e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄지는 다양합니다. 이번 이미지는 흑지에 투명 실크인쇄로 처리된 건입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a7f989f4-78eb-4092-ade6-651735a06c3d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223939367562/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-516a8f93-2d60-405b-9784-d9a7808cb7d2\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ee7c6c35-33ca-47d0-9981-43d371699345\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3e8b560d-0e3b-4bae-9888-dcfc182a70fb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f4d69d44-bc3c-4562-91b9-cd16335e9305\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄지에 갱판지를 합지하여 작업을 진행합니다. 갱판지는 1000g이 일반적입니다. 하지만 더 견고하고 단단하게 작업을 하려면 1200g으로 업그레이드가 가능합니다. 다만 모든 싸바리 박스는 습도에 약합니다. 휨 현상이 발생할 수 있으므로 접착과 바람을 빼는 작업이 꼼꼼히 필요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-604d7db7-ef08-413e-a67c-96ac74766c6f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0b0d4858-b5c7-4aaa-88cd-fd492b9bf0ce\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1f66225f-d5cb-4bb5-abed-24dffb59d29d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-98964531-2be7-42fa-906f-9dc6825c7156\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>중짝</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f3def97d-7e58-42c4-a5f3-9ce444545186\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0d2c2560-11ca-46e3-ad48-970ae0d48663\" style=\"color:#555555;\">중간 부분은 2단 싸바리의 경우 하단에 해당합니다. 3단은 이 중단에 하단의 박스를 한 번 더 덧씌우는 것입니다. 강력한 접착제로 하단 박스를 중단 박스에 부착하는 겁니다. 그러므로 2단 싸바리보다 3단 싸바리가 더 비싸고 견고합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c1a7ce17-2f7b-4004-9d67-d09a432bc416\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c5cbe080-9e59-42cd-8d48-db18bf4d9476\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-79e1a8e5-3cec-4f0b-b156-db1466601623\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f875b46a-db81-482f-95c9-4a5c196c83a2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 중간 부분을 1/2위치에 맞춰 제작할 수 있고 하단을 더 높은 위치에 제작할 수도 있습니다. 통상의 경우 중간에 위치하도록 만듭니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5c16f054-43fb-4fb5-bfd6-79017b895d28\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223939367562/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b6833fe1-3179-4027-a0fa-34d7de2f9d5e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-48e65b28-abad-46be-8825-3e7036fd2abc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-abbbe4b8-32f7-425c-8e57-180aef7633c5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-932b1379-7b77-4c55-b28b-a4abbcc156a5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fedef1d1-bab8-4375-a950-c5553a5d93ce\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>하짝</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7c944427-e95c-44dd-b820-03d5f34bc4a3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b05f3072-6626-415c-85dd-bad7da827fe5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">맨 하단은 중짝에 강력 접착제로 부착합니다. 하단에 제품의 정보를 인쇄하는 경우가 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b095cef7-410e-4473-8180-da204d856648\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223939367562/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c5d3f637-ae88-4d94-a03a-0659a3324eac\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:671px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223939367562/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-52101c5d-9ff1-4227-9b3b-049b4ecf8d81\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dd886cfa-45e0-4246-b4a0-f4e349cd11ed\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e1db13da-495f-48e2-8619-819a4bf4a075\" style=\"color:#555555;\">정보를 넣는 부분은 하단이나 상짝의 안쪽밖에 없습니다. 디자인 작업 시 주의하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-86510a7c-f7a7-44ee-a1e5-51cc689b5692\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-df780a04-3602-415f-96f4-d4660e651577\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-c19a135d-0dac-4a17-a392-b6c62ce80c72\" style=\"\">내부 종이 패드</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e2ac7fd9-3247-4d4e-b849-dc0b80a4d365\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223939367562/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cb41bb50-adb1-45e4-b13a-717e1c48b844\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3a90e8a1-a527-4e4b-9466-1ac475f7e6d1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-765f1885-de41-4e69-8fab-f17dadd54d68\" style=\"color:#555555;\">내부에 제품을 넣기 위해 그 모양을 따서 담을 수 있는 패드를 만듭니다. 이 패드는 종이로 만들 수도 있고 스티로폼으로 제작할 수도 있습니다. 플라스틱으로도 제작되기도 하며 나무로도 만들 수도 있습니다. 너무도 다양하여 패드 종류의 모양과 방법은 나열하기 어렵습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b1110a18-5cb3-4e01-9596-6f9debbabb84\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7b91b328-172e-4855-ba93-d28c2932f46a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5e9d2cef-9c91-4ab8-8384-2aa1bc9eb4bd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-29a7c8e4-7133-4278-a6b1-07409b19f5a3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">내부 패드를 제작할 때 주의 사항입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7a351b32-a028-4618-be43-57f9f4456c8b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-69b0e939-fe36-4e4c-a640-87048ddf2192\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4f4a918d-69d7-4af9-99da-9abd19dd6638\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a42c3291-a991-4800-854e-cdd195f84371\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가장 좋은 방법은 제품을 받아서 제작하는 것입니다. 문서나 측정을 통해서도 만들 수는 있겠으나 곡면이나 정확한 모양을 만들려면 제품을 수령하여 목형 제작 회사가 모양을 따서 제작하는 것이 중요합니다. 천바리(?)로 감싸지도 하고 다른 방식으로도 제작할 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eb5f5049-0387-40a3-ae88-841e41ffa265\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7d89ae75-dc67-4d66-95df-8859e0dc80c7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-98c0fef1-7a8f-4e75-8b05-3246a62d15ce\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a16e3f52-115d-4ada-82f6-d5fd2f55a964\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이 패드와 융단을 이어 붙이는 작업이 수작업으로 제작되는 경우가 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d8f2000e-b1a0-4d6f-b08e-514ffa6c70a2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:652px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223939367562/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-966f4882-e923-4da9-8510-d23b1739ad6e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-89b19da6-6b80-4a61-9fdf-c6511d084006\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-58291391-d692-460c-86b8-a1d99c773e4e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하단 패드와 융단을 강력한 테이핑으로 붙여서 연결합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b1760f8e-a410-4958-980e-78064336fcc8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:634px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223939367562/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a86b74c4-dbd6-48df-99d5-5fee1097d384\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-59eba2de-3a37-49a4-bafc-3c94f64712ed\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e6f49a87-a861-4086-9753-e9efabec4b47\" style=\"color:#555555;\">내부에 삽입되는 모양과 가짓수는 너무나 다양합니다. 공진단 60개가 들어가는 모양일 수도 있고 제품을 담는 것이 아니라 끼워서 구분만 하는 모양으로도 제작이 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-71dc3e18-344f-4e25-b5e8-9f088b275911\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-29a61d7d-cefc-4147-9ce5-3a74ed54d050\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-91b82768-3c70-47d8-abf9-8c708616e473\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7048be2a-763d-4686-b316-9f3750268522\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 모든 사항은 (주)파파스컴퍼니과 상의하고 결정하시기 바랍니다. 거래 여부를 떠나 싸바리에 대한 모든 정보를 안내드리도록 하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-62bec7e4-6640-4888-b7cf-834eb399d441\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223939367562/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-62cc1708-6e09-422b-9ffb-f74ebc9ef1ab\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6d3321c5-d7c7-4878-9868-5b2578ff7814\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a76afd82-5195-4d25-b278-598ef754430a\" style=\"\">제작 사항</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f981fa0e-3b06-402d-b06d-1f0299a21e09\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-722f6f43-963f-438f-bc53-4489d5aa7240\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a5e572ca-48b2-4efc-ac55-c426043d6a73\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>형태</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d0491b8d-4bd9-487e-a615-281bf88d6e69\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 3단 싸바리 박스</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6c5b3e1e-a5a6-4109-b9db-c25e97d5e11e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-88973cc0-fb96-43b4-bb2c-a62e72eace69\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>외부 종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a4df38e5-8007-4ce2-9906-46e4ddbd2765\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 에코블랙 120g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d13e0339-5139-42ab-ab0e-5fa2f04bcbbc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7bb9de57-bf41-4f10-a5b9-de24f6eb9825\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>합지 종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e84fc46c-1439-4a25-9881-5caf42084665\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 상/하짝 1200g, 중짝 1000g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c95e718b-8b6d-4649-9c25-7ec5668ff62b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-836c94cc-0704-466f-9110-a4359ad72097\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e1f3073c-4bde-467b-b833-b971a10881ee\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 없음</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-136535d9-1223-4ffc-adef-0fa4e9416771\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e78ca8cd-bc4b-4250-a1b1-fe7fd28ca5a4\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄 후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1b3d0ec9-12ad-446a-9a4e-4b50d2157424\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 상짝 투명 실크인쇄</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b1979c78-26e6-48bb-90fd-af87e6590d63\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1d1f81ee-2335-44ee-afda-f6b9dde29b92\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기본 후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5201c8b8-8766-4a14-93d0-203c29122a15\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 목형 + 톰슨(도무송) + 합지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e762906a-65da-44ff-b407-b5f5cecacdf2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-62c6c992-3bbb-468d-8d93-b16854317f26\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>추가</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3fb27eac-d704-40c6-995e-c353dcca6d94\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 종이 갱판지 패드 + 검정 융단</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2f5ba261-e870-4797-b644-aba0c3b5d8b2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f1d196f2-64c1-4225-b7f2-d7f6ef30a9a7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>수량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5745a32b-078a-4b07-aa20-a9ae44918e24\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 최소 수량 (별도 문의)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3fdc8205-c9e8-4885-bfd5-5e2a2c27688f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ee4c8023-4892-4c27-83dd-9c1b61c0ecdc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>납기</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-013f1d81-58da-4fbc-93fc-5b9821fff3cd\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 주문 후 7일 이내 초 긴급 납품</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-78436b37-5ca2-453c-b244-0d184a1d4c1f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f188c841-aaf4-44f7-bfe2-04014ba9398a\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c4093a9d-2d79-46ed-826a-5af0fc4adbf8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c8e7935c-6973-4e14-b0c9-f177d15d7cfa\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>금액</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d1561a64-6dc6-49b3-9340-76714fe8f360\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"> : 별도 문의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-efe765f8-8051-4da7-9dd3-d5bdc22d9590\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d7dc961f-1d00-482f-a1a4-987f60697c4a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c35cb07-3e3f-4f45-b98b-ce2faef970eb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7abab15b-cbc1-4c14-8583-1e4b60bdff9b\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 종합인쇄 전문 회사입니다. 모든 작업을 고객의 기준으로 생각하며 진행합니다. 고객이 주문한 인쇄물이 궁금한지... 물건이 이상 없이 제날짜에 납품될 수 있는지... 변경사항이 발생하면 어떻게 처리해 주시는지... 등등을 항상 고객의 관점에서 진행하려고 노력하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-07540930-e29a-4657-8098-98b80b462b9f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7deda9c0-4352-45dd-82c7-28471064f9f9\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2d89f2f3-0126-4895-96a2-68facec44d5a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1b0280b0-6e76-495c-bce3-61a505951eb7\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">물론 모든 사항을 고객의 입장에만 맞춰 작업해 드릴 수는 없습니다. 하지만 최소한 고객이 무엇을 바라는지 아니면 어떤 부분에 대해 고충이 있는지를 면밀하게 검토하여 소통하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ad977e09-daa7-4f97-903b-64cea5e81480\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6a4c786a-9f16-472c-9162-9acde750a875\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9c53f468-8fe4-429e-86cd-07c2a2a4fa5f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-716df857-802a-46e4-b984-9b90b9961c88\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니이 생각하는 최고의 서비스는 고객과의 소통이라고 생각합니다. 단가면 단가, 납기면 납기 등을 항상 고객의 입장에서 고민하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d3659a9d-8fd5-4627-8e94-ad45e3149365\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dbbe53ea-866d-41db-a118-80eb76cf1e25\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9ad8ab85-d2f9-45d7-b62d-7e25875f7e47\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c26022a1-edb9-4a03-ba02-1111b8cc3b9b\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">인쇄의 모든 부분에 대해 언제든지 궁금한 것이 있으시면 문의하시기 바랍니다. 특별한 시간과 요일을 제외하고는 모든 문의에 대해 정보 공유 차원에서 소통하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7bd6f169-550c-46d8-a51a-c09e37c1559b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223939367562/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-364dcdda-6c07-42aa-a5f7-3f3628914ba6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223939367562/011.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-79eba2a2-27d6-46f0-a2d7-3e8b209e30d5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-31c83cab-ab04-4137-b68b-cc42c03862b8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24ae41f1-f8fb-4147-9278-5edd398743cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
